<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Gavel of Justice Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Talk to Shamus Felligan in Halas to receive the quest. <BR>
<BR>
2) Head out to the Goblin igloos in Everfrost and hunt Ice Goblin Casters.   They will drop either Caster Beads or Shattered Caster Beads.<BR>
<BR>
3) Return Caster Beads to Shamus to receive the Gavel of Justice.  <BR>
<BR>
This quest may only be available to low-level characters.</div>
<BR>
