<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Dayhawk</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-08-21 20:59:00</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>If you are a shaman don't do this quest, there is a quest to get a neckless which has infinte charges of a magical hammer with the same stats as this weapon and it takes about 15 mins to do the quest, you get the quest off Cindll in the leather shop in Halas. <BR>
<BR>
Hail Cindll and say "What mammoth hide parchment" and she will give you the parchment.<BR>
<BR>
Go to Greta across from Cindll's shop she is the lone merchant, hail her and say "What ink" and she will give you the ink.<BR>
<BR>
Go to the shaman guild and give the parchment and the ink to Jinkus he will then give you a wanted poster.<BR>
<BR>
Now go to Qeynos and give the wanted poster to the guard inside the bank he will give you a list.<BR>
<BR>
Now go back to Halas and give the list to Jinkus and he gives you the neckless, I dont remember the stats of the neckless but the hammer is good<BR>
 <BR>
Hope this helps.<BR>
<BR>
PS. I tryed the gravel of justice quest for 8 and a half hours and all I got were a load of shattered beads. Although It wasn't all bad because I made about 10pp out of the shattered beads.</font></td></tr></table>
<BR>
